text: Pawlikowice may refer to the following places in Poland: *Pawlikowice, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Pawlikowice, Kutno County in Łódź Voivodeship (central Poland) *Pawlikowice, Pabianice County in Łódź Voivodeship (central Poland) *Pawlikowice, Lesser Poland Voivodeship (south Poland)
title: Pawlikowice
